snippet.title: EVERYTHING WRONG WITH HARRY AND MEGHAN (How to tell if you're in a relationship with a Narcissist)
snippet.description:
The key to Understanding Meghan Markle and all of her troubles with her friends, her family, her marriage, the press the people is to look at the Six traits that make her a narcissist!

How can you tell is someone is a narcissist? Narcissists are the hardest people to be in a relationship with. While it starts off great, as the relationship continues, it becomes more hellish, as it seems to be what Prince Harry is discovering with Meghan Markle. Well, is Meghan Markle a narcissist? Why is Meghan Markle popular? Is it earned or is it by design?

In this video I look at the six traits commonly found in a narcissist, as well as look at the ways that Meghan has carefully cultivated the right image for herself. 

*****
Disclaimer - the content of this and all of my videos are my opinions based on detailed research that I have performed. Please do you own research before you make up you own mind.
